sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: User Login and Dashboard Access

    User->>Route: GET / (unauthenticated)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward to oauth-proxy
    OAuth->>OSAuth: Redirect to OAuth login<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Client Secret Auth
    User->>OSAuth: Submit credentials<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    OSAuth-->>OAuth: OAuth authorization code
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy to backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>OAuth token in header
    Backend-->>OAuth: React SPA (static assets)
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>User: Dashboard UI<br/>TLS1.2+ with OAuth cookie

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: API Request to Kubernetes

    User->>Route: POST /api/notebooks<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OAuth cookie
    Route->>OAuth: TLS termination
    OAuth->>Backend: 8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Bearer token in header
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Namespace<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Namespace created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create RoleBinding<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: RoleBinding created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR created
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>User: Success notification<br/>TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Metrics Monitoring

    Prometheus->>Route: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Route->>OAuth: Service cert TLS
    OAuth->>Backend: 8080/TCP HTTP<br/>skip-auth-regex bypass
    Backend->>Prometheus: Query metrics<br/>9092/TCP HTTP<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Prometheus-->>Backend: Metrics data
    Backend-->>OAuth: Prometheus format metrics
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Prometheus: Metrics scraped

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: WebSocket for Real-time Updates

    User->>Route: WSS /wss/k8s/notebooks<br/>443/TCP WSS<br/>OAuth cookie
    Route->>OAuth: Upgrade to WebSocket
    OAuth->>Backend: WS 8080/TCP<br/>Bearer token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Stream events
    Backend-->>OAuth: WebSocket events
    OAuth-->>Route: WSS events
    Route-->>User: Real-time status updates
